1783650418965522	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy6hQ		item.create	bn-50xb	{"description":"Runner updated stable to rustc 1.97.0 (2026-07-07); new lint useless_borrows_in_formatting fires on crates/maw-assurance/src/oracle_a.rs:301 (&origin.tip in format! args). First surfaced by the new sg2-bench-clippy lane (bn-1nmh) since it is the first CI lane compiling maw-assurance under clippy. Local toolchain is 1.96 so local checks pass — same drift class as bn-zox8. Fix the borrow; sweep for other new-lint sites once a 1.97 toolchain is available locally.","kind":"bug","title":"fix(ci): clippy 1.97 useless_borrows_in_formatting in maw-assurance oracle_a (sg2-bench-clippy red)"}	blake3:UoGUaOKGhh4nrpQG6NIYtJFYALLFh9rZMJ0lZurBhis
