1783707987039817	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEygRU		item.create	bn-1q7x	{"description":"Found by the bn-1lhb worker: the Justfile check recipe runs cargo test on the root maw-workspaces package only, so integration tests under crates/maw-cli/tests/ (undo_cli.rs from bn-117s, epoch_lock_cli.rs from bn-13rc) never run in just check or CI. They pass under 'cargo test -p maw-cli'. Fix: either add 'cargo test -p maw-cli' (or --workspace) to the check recipe with an eye on runtime, or relocate those test files to the root tests/ dir like tests/post_sync_hook_bn_1lhb.rs did. Related: bn-1n2b (CI lane-wiring meta-test) covers the recipe-to-workflow gap; this is the recipe-to-package gap. Same silent-rot class as bn-1nmh.","kind":"bug","title":"just check does not run crates/maw-cli/tests/ — undo_cli.rs + epoch_lock_cli.rs are CI-ungated"}	blake3:puklnpb_WGsagtp4rb8_JaGBHy5G3Q7tnFUErwzggBU
